146
00:10:24,498 --> 00:10:25,625
Se nos divertir,

147
00:10:26,167 --> 00:10:27,710
pode sobreviver.

148
00:10:29,503 --> 00:10:31,213
Certo. Minha história?

149
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:34,175
